          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two targets of Th-23O, with densities of approx. 50mug/",
                "cm**2 and approx. 300 mug/cm**2 and Th-232 contents of",
                "less or equal 0.1% and 8.5%, respectively, on approx.",
                "50 mug.Cm**2 carbon backing.",
                "A Th-232 target with a density of 230 mug/cm**2 on a",
                "12 mug/cm**2 carbon backing.",
                "Targets of U-234 and U-238 with densities of approx.",
                "50 mug/cm**2 and approx. 80 mug/cm**2 on nickel",
                "backing of unknown densities and with unknown isotopic",
                "compositions. The content of U-234 in the U-236 target",
                "was less or equal 0.1% and that the target contained",
                "approx. 10% of tungsten.",
                "Two target of U-238 from which one had a density of",
                "approx. 200 mug/cm**2 on a approx. 40 mug.Cm**2 carbon",
                "backing.   The second one consisted of a mixture of U-C",
                "and U-C/2 on a 44 mug/cm**2 carbon backing,",
                "corresponding to approx.  100 mug/cm**2 U-238, depleted",
                "in U-235 to approx.  0.3%, plus approx.  70 mug/cm**2",
                "of carbon."
              ]
            }
          ],
